attributes.description: Dashboard providing statistics about Domains and IP Addresses type indicators from the abuse.ch integration

params.markdown:
**Overview**

The dashboard provides a comprehensive view of threat indicators across Domain and IP Addresses. The Indicators by Confidence pie chart shows the distribution of indicators based on their confidence levels, helping to assess reliability. The Indicators by IP and Indicators by Name bar charts highlight the most frequently flagged IP addresses and threat names, giving insight into common sources and types of threats. The Indicators by Software Name pie chart reveals which software is most often targeted, while the Indicators by Malware bar chart shows the prevalence of different malware families. Finally, the Indicators over Time line chart tracks trends and spikes in malicious activity, offering visibility into threat patterns over time.
